IAC - Infrastructure as Code
defined in code
stored in source control
Declarative - terraform is declarative {}
Imperative
Idempotent & consistent - it won't change its state

Benefits:
	Automated Deployment
	Consistent Environment
	Repeatable Process
	Reusable Components
	Documented Architecture
Terraform Components:
	Terraform Executables
	Terraform file
